Rally Round The Av, Bois


2014-11-07 @ The Pirate Bay around thewaymouth aka mikedreams on: Gotta Have Av's Best Week Ever Never Stops Until The Living End... 


- Day In The Zone (Annual Festival 2002, c/o The Zone 100.5 FM Sacramento).


- Raley Field is the home of the Sacramento River Cats minor league baseball team in the Pacific Coast League. The stadium has 11,093 permanent seats and grass berms in both right and left field for a total capacity of 14,014. Its original capacity in 2002 was 14,611.


- Avril's debut CD Let Go dropped that week, June 4. 


So great to have a hot AUD / pop-rockin set from so early in her dear career.

